# Surge RULE-SET (GITHUB)
# Target Policy: Proxy
# Purpose:
# - Force GitHub related traffic through Proxy when needed
#
# Recommended order in Surge [Rule]:
#   ...
#   RULE-SET,https://jovanykoch.github.io/loon/rules/github.list,Proxy
#   ...

DOMAIN-SUFFIX,github.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,githubassets.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,githubapp.com

DOMAIN,api.github.com
DOMAIN,raw.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,github.io